   - Pros: Catecholamine excess symptoms and elevated normetanephrine are classic for paraganglioma; intense SSTR expression on 68Ga-DOTATATE PET is characteristic; location in right adnexa/paracervical region is plausible for extra-adrenal paraganglioma; imaging findings consistent with hypervascular mass with necrosis; no invasion of adjacent structures.
