   - No communication with vessel or vascular flow; does not show Doppler flow patterns described.  
7) Seroma  
   - No vascular communication or Doppler flow.  
8) Lymphocele  
   - No vascular communication; typically lymphatic.  
9) Neoplasm  
   - Could appear cystic, but no vascular flow or communication; not consistent with to-and-fro pattern.  

